latestIgtvVideos.title: HIFU(High Intensity Focussed Ultrasound)
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
HOW DOES HIFU WORK?
HIFU uses focussed ultrasound rays which heat up at at specific depths to breakdown and rebuild collagen and elastin. As we age there is reduced production of collagen making our skin loose and face sag.
WHAT DOES HIFU DO?
One of the most effective Nonsurgical Noninvasive face lifting technology:
* Lifting of face
* Lifting of cheeks
* Eyebrow lifting
* Nasolabial folds reduction
* Jawline slimming
* Double chin reduction 
* Wrinkle reduction
* Turkey neck correction 
* Smooth wing of skin
* Slimming of face
HOW DOES IT FEEL?
It is a very comfortable noninvasive almost painless procedure which takes 45 min - 1 hour. Sometimes a session is repeated in 1-3 months and the effect stays for 1-1.5 years.
WHO CAN GET HIFU DONE?
Anyone who is 30 plus and needs face lifting can get it done. For very old patients or patients who have excessive skin laxity we prefer to combine it with RF sessions.
SIDE EFFECTS:
There can be mild swelling, rarely bruising or numbing sensation. Side effects are less common and if happen recover in 1-2 weeks.

Your Skin Deserves a Workout Routine Too! 💦🧴 – Here are some Skincare Tips for Fitness Lovers.

Hitting the gym or heading for a run? Don’t forget your skincare preps!
✅ DO: Always start with a clean face. Apply a light serum and don’t skip your sunscreen—even indoors.
✅ DO: Tie your hair back to avoid sweat and oil buildup.
❌ DON’T: Touch your face during your workout—it spreads bacteria.
✅ DO: Wash your hands and face immediately after you’re done to prevent clogged pores or breakouts.

Glowing skin needs discipline—just like your body. 🧘‍♀️✨

Glutathione – It’s More Than Just a Skin Brightener.

Often mistaken as just a “fairness” solution, Glutathione is actually one of the most powerful antioxidants your body can benefit from. When combined with Vitamin C, it plays a vital role in detoxifying cells, improving immunity, and reducing oxidative stress.

It’s commonly used in supportive care for patients with cancer, HIV, liver diseases, and chronic fatigue, helping them manage inflammation and cellular damage.

Exposure to pollution, UV rays, and daily stress increases free radicals in our body—and that’s where Glutathione steps in, neutralizing the damage and promoting overall wellness from within.

💉 For brighter skin, better health, and stronger immunity—this isn’t just cosmetic, it’s clinical.
